        <em style="font: bold italic 15px arial; color: #5c020a;">Chef Email of the Week</em>
        <p style="font: 12px arial; color: #333;">
          I really would like to cook more meals at home.  I am single and 36.  The thought of spending time to shop, prepare foods, cook, and then clean keeps me from doing anything.  I am interested in using your website. . .<br />
