        </p>
        <p style="font: bold italic 15px arial; color: #5c020a;">Chef response:</p>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>Thanks for your interest! My suggestion: sign up for our service for a month. If you don't find it helpful you can cancel before 30 days and get your money back.</p>
        <p>I hear you when you list all that goes into meal prep...unfortunately that's just how it is. Like anything that's worthwhile, meal preparation takes time. With Chef service you don't have to search recipes, put together a menu and then make up a shopping list. This alone will save you lots of time!</p>
        <p>Also, please believe me when I say that if you will make meals consistently (perhaps 2-3 times a week and work up from there) they will become much easier.</p>
        <p>Good luck to you and we look forward to having you as a member of Everything but the Chef.</p>
